#### Q21. How do you destructure the properties that are sent to the Dish component?

```javascript
function Dish(props) {
  return (
    <h1>
      {props.name} {props.cookingTime}
    </h1>
  );
}
```

- %OPTION% `function Dish([name, cookingTime]) { return <h1>{name} {cookingTime}</h1>; }`
- %OPTION% `function Dish({name, cookingTime}) { return <h1>{name} {cookingTime}</h1>; }`
- %OPTION% `function Dish(props) { return <h1>{name} {cookingTime}</h1>; }`
- %OPTION% `function Dish(...props) { return <h1>{name} {cookingTime}</h1>; }`

